description: Thinking about EVERYTHING as life passes by. Am I right? Am I wrong? Should I listen to a song about how everyone should get along? Should I just get along with my day? Questions that often long for answers. Idle times bring out the truth which is why most of us stay as busy as possible. Proof that even walking around obstacles serve as a possible solution to pollution...
